Poison needles?

20
00:01:55,870 --> 00:01:57,430
I've been perceptive my entire life.

21
00:01:59,840 --> 00:02:00,840
I never expected this to happen.

22
00:02:01,640 --> 00:02:03,040
I'm truly old and senile now.

23
00:02:04,430 --> 00:02:06,560
I've brought disaster upon myself.

24
00:02:07,870 --> 00:02:09,680
First, he harmed
Ji Jingtang and his family.

25
00:02:10,030 --> 00:02:11,360
After that, he turned Abbess into a mute.

26
00:02:11,680 --> 00:02:12,190
And now,

27
00:02:12,360 --> 00:02:13,960
he's even trying to kill me and Tianlei.

28
00:02:14,710 --> 00:02:15,360
Grandmother,

29
00:02:15,630 --> 00:02:17,520
if we allow him to get his way

30
00:02:17,520 --> 00:02:18,520
and continue his reign,

31
00:02:19,240 --> 00:02:20,400
our family lineage

32
00:02:20,630 --> 00:02:22,190
will end here.

33
00:02:25,120 --> 00:02:27,280
I'm truly old and senile.

34
00:02:32,240 --> 00:02:32,870
Grandmother,

35
00:02:33,750 --> 00:02:35,280
but it's not too late for us
to do something about it.

36
00:02:37,120 --> 00:02:38,360
What do you mean?

37
00:02:38,870 --> 00:02:40,080
I wish to use his trick against him.

38
00:02:40,520 --> 00:02:42,520
I will let Ke Shizhao commit
one more evil deed.

39
00:02:43,870 --> 00:02:45,310
You want him to commit another evil deed?

40
00:02:47,840 --> 00:02:48,960
We must make him

41
00:02:48,960 --> 00:02:50,520
expose his true goals himself.

42
00:02:51,310 --> 00:02:52,400
Let's talk about my medicine,
which was poisoned.

43
00:02:52,750 --> 00:02:54,710
He never kept the dregs
of the medicine he brewed.

44
00:02:54,710 --> 00:02:56,080
He will surely deny it.

45
00:02:56,470 --> 00:02:57,240
Besides, we didn't see him

46
00:02:57,750 --> 00:02:59,590
placing the poison needles personally.

47
00:02:59,750 --> 00:03:01,150
Wang Huzi will surely deny it too.

48
00:03:01,750 --> 00:03:03,360
He'd say that Yansheng was seeing things.

49
00:03:03,960 --> 00:03:05,560
That's why we have to capture
Ke Shizhao red-handed

50
00:03:05,560 --> 00:03:07,680
in order to expose him.

51
00:03:18,080 --> 00:03:18,630
Liu...

52
00:03:21,590 --> 00:03:22,190
Yansheng?

53
00:03:22,840 --> 00:03:23,310
You...

54
00:03:25,310 --> 00:03:26,240
Were you looking for me?

55
00:03:36,240 --> 00:03:36,960
Mr. Liu.

56
00:03:37,430 --> 00:03:38,280
You're back.

57
00:03:39,150 --> 00:03:40,000
Long time no see.

58
00:03:47,680 --> 00:03:48,400
Mr. Liu,

59
00:03:48,840 --> 00:03:50,150
I have pressing matters to attend to.

60
00:03:50,150 --> 00:03:51,400
I shall take my leave.

61
00:04:01,360 --> 00:04:01,910
Yansheng.

62
00:04:09,120 --> 00:04:09,710
Grandmother.

63
00:04:10,520 --> 00:04:11,360
I've been pretending

64
00:04:11,910 --> 00:04:13,470
to be a mute all these years.

65
00:04:15,840 --> 00:04:17,830
Hurry and tell Old Madam why you did so.

66
00:04:19,480 --> 00:04:21,120
It happened three years ago.

67
00:04:22,390 --> 00:04:24,240
Back then, it was a rainy summer night.

68
00:04:24,800 --> 00:04:26,270
I was passing by the courtyard.

69
00:05:33,600 --> 00:05:34,310
Good girl.

70
00:05:34,310 --> 00:05:36,160
Hurry. Get up and speak.

71
00:05:41,430 --> 00:05:42,270
Yansheng,

72
00:05:42,480 --> 00:05:43,360
if that's the case,

73
00:05:43,360 --> 00:05:45,040
why didn't you
tell Grandmother what happened?

74
00:05:45,120 --> 00:05:46,360
Why did you pretend to be mute, then?

75
00:05:48,480 --> 00:05:49,190
Initially,

76
00:05:49,430 --> 00:05:51,720
I wanted to tell Old Madam
about it the next day.

77
00:05:52,240 --> 00:05:52,870
However,

78
00:05:53,600 --> 00:05:55,560
Fang Xiaoqiao saw that I was panicking.

79
00:05:55,800 --> 00:05:57,270
She told me to stay in the room.

80
00:05:57,870 --> 00:06:00,560
After that, Ke Shizhao arrived.

81
00:06:01,190 --> 00:06:02,600
He tried to fish information out of me.

82
00:06:02,830 --> 00:06:04,160
I kept my composure

83
00:06:04,160 --> 00:06:05,480
and didn't tell him a single thing.

84
00:06:06,310 --> 00:06:07,920
Ke Shizhao was suspicious of me.

85
00:06:07,920 --> 00:06:09,000
He threatened me

86
00:06:09,480 --> 00:06:12,040
by saying that he was
already ruling the Qi family.

87
00:06:12,750 --> 00:06:14,240
Big Brother and Second Brother

88
00:06:14,560 --> 00:06:16,160
were already dead.

89
00:06:16,920 --> 00:06:18,830
And, Tianlei's life was in danger too.

90
00:06:20,000 --> 00:06:22,600
He said I must obey him
if I want to survive in this residence

91
00:06:24,480 --> 00:06:25,920
together with Mother.

92
00:06:28,600 --> 00:06:29,830
He went overboard.

93
00:06:30,360 --> 00:06:31,920
How could he threaten you like that?

94
00:06:32,480 --> 00:06:33,190
After that,

95
00:06:34,040 --> 00:06:36,480
although Ke Shizhao didn't know
what I saw that night,

96
00:06:37,000 --> 00:06:38,830
he threatened me
both directly and indirectly

97
00:06:39,040 --> 00:06:40,800
by saying
that my mother's health wasn't well.

98
00:06:41,600 --> 00:06:43,310
He wanted me to take care of her

99
00:06:43,800 --> 00:06:45,600
and stay out of the Qi family's affairs.

100
00:06:46,160 --> 00:06:46,800
I was afraid.

101
00:06:47,240 --> 00:06:49,040
I was afraid that he would
target my mother

102
00:06:49,600 --> 00:06:51,600
if I told you the truth.

103
00:06:51,920 --> 00:06:52,600
That's why I...

104
00:06:55,870 --> 00:06:57,600
I remember that you had a high fever
for several days

105
00:06:58,240 --> 00:06:59,310
after Second Brother's death.

106
00:07:00,000 --> 00:07:01,390
You turned into a mute when you woke up.

107
00:07:02,270 --> 00:07:03,040
So, Yansheng,

108
00:07:03,830 --> 00:07:04,560
you pretended to be mute

109
00:07:04,560 --> 00:07:05,920
in order to dispel Ke Shizhao's doubt

110
00:07:06,480 --> 00:07:07,800
and protect yourself

111
00:07:07,800 --> 00:07:08,920
and your mother.

112
00:07:15,950 --> 00:07:18,870
How could I be so muddle-headed?

113
00:07:19,870 --> 00:07:23,120
I actually believed in the words
of a cunning fox!

114
00:07:23,600 --> 00:07:26,950
I was the reason he was able
to kill my grandsons!

115
00:07:27,630 --> 00:07:29,070
And my granddaughter
had to suffer so much

116
00:07:29,070 --> 00:07:31,510
because of me!

117
00:07:32,680 --> 00:07:34,360
I'm sorry, my child.

118
00:07:35,390 --> 00:07:36,680
I'm sorry.

119
00:07:38,160 --> 00:07:40,120
Tianlei, I'm sorry.

120
00:07:40,390 --> 00:07:42,070
I'm sorry.

121
00:07:43,510 --> 00:07:48,600
I've let down the ancestors
of the Qi family!

122
00:07:58,240 --> 00:07:58,870
Grandmother,

123
00:08:00,040 --> 00:08:01,310
you don't need to blame yourself for it.

124
00:08:02,480 --> 00:08:03,680
Since you've understood the true nature of

125
00:08:03,680 --> 00:08:05,000
that scheming man,

126
00:08:05,680 --> 00:08:07,190
that means
it's not too late for us to turn back.

127
00:08:08,680 --> 00:08:09,360
Grandmother,

128
00:08:09,680 --> 00:08:11,240
you still have us with you.

129
00:08:14,510 --> 00:08:15,190
All right.

130
00:08:17,830 --> 00:08:19,560
I can hang in there

131
00:08:21,160 --> 00:08:22,920
with you guys around.

132
00:08:24,480 --> 00:08:25,310
In my opinion,

133
00:08:26,070 --> 00:08:27,720
let's use his trick against him

134
00:08:28,720 --> 00:08:29,950
and drive him into a corner.

135
00:09:14,240 --> 00:09:14,870
Tianlei?

136
00:09:18,600 --> 00:09:19,200
Bingyan?

137
00:09:25,150 --> 00:09:25,790
Finally.

138
00:09:28,840 --> 00:09:30,150
Both of you are finally dead!

139
00:10:10,790 --> 00:10:12,150
Someone!

140
00:10:13,390 --> 00:10:14,030
Young Master.

141
00:10:14,320 --> 00:10:15,440
Summon Wang Huzi.

142
00:10:15,630 --> 00:10:16,150
Yes, Young Master.

143
00:10:30,390 --> 00:10:31,030
Young Master,

144
00:10:31,550 --> 00:10:32,320
were you looking for me?

145
00:10:34,630 --> 00:10:36,080
Why isn't there any news of their passing

146
00:10:36,840 --> 00:10:38,080
after so long?

147
00:10:38,080 --> 00:10:38,550
I...

148
00:10:38,790 --> 00:10:40,630
I did place the poison needles
on their bed.

149
00:10:40,870 --> 00:10:41,870
Could it be

150
00:10:41,870 --> 00:10:43,270
that they haven't
returned to their room yet?

151
00:10:45,550 --> 00:10:47,030
Did something go wrong

152
00:10:47,390 --> 00:10:48,390
because of your ineptitude again?

153
00:10:48,870 --> 00:10:50,080
Young Master, don't worry.

154
00:10:50,080 --> 00:10:52,200
Nothing ever goes wrong
when I complete a task.

155
00:10:53,270 --> 00:10:53,790
Tell me.

156
00:10:54,320 --> 00:10:55,440
Were you seen by anyone

157
00:10:56,080 --> 00:10:57,200
when you placed the poison needles?

158
00:10:57,550 --> 00:10:58,960
I swear! No one saw me!

159
00:10:58,960 --> 00:11:00,390
Only you and I

160
00:11:00,390 --> 00:11:01,270
know about this!

161
00:11:01,440 --> 00:11:03,320
No one else saw me!

162
00:11:04,030 --> 00:11:04,630
I swear.

163
00:11:05,120 --> 00:11:05,630
Come here.

164
00:11:08,080 --> 00:11:09,910
Shouldn't you head to their chamber
and observe them

165
00:11:10,080 --> 00:11:11,630
to see if you completed the deed or not?

166
00:11:11,790 --> 00:11:13,390
Yes, Young Master.

167
00:11:21,020 --> 00:11:21,770
Over there!

168
00:11:21,770 --> 00:11:23,410
Search that area thoroughly!

169
00:11:23,810 --> 00:11:24,260
Okay.

170
00:11:24,810 --> 00:11:26,140
You, search over there!

171
00:11:26,340 --> 00:11:27,460
That's right. Over there.

172
00:11:27,860 --> 00:11:28,690
Did you find it?

173
00:11:29,020 --> 00:11:29,690
To the right!

174
00:11:29,690 --> 00:11:30,890
That's right! That's the spot!

175
00:11:43,100 --> 00:11:43,650
Look.

176
00:11:43,770 --> 00:11:45,290
I told you Wang Huzi would come, right?

177
00:11:46,170 --> 00:11:47,570
I'm sure he'll be scared to death

178
00:11:47,890 --> 00:11:48,930
if we show ourselves right now.

179
00:11:50,170 --> 00:11:52,340
He'd surely think that we came back to life.

180
00:11:57,690 --> 00:11:58,930
Search that spot!

181
00:11:58,930 --> 00:11:59,740
Did you find it?

182
00:12:00,620 --> 00:12:02,340
You, search over there!

183
00:12:02,770 --> 00:12:03,410
Search over there!

184
00:12:03,410 --> 00:12:04,460
Do a thorough search!

185
00:12:04,930 --> 00:12:06,570
You two, do a thorough search!

186
00:12:08,570 --> 00:12:09,460
Did you find it?

187
00:12:11,410 --> 00:12:12,050
It's here!

188
00:12:12,340 --> 00:12:13,170
I found it!

189
00:12:13,290 --> 00:12:13,930
Hurry!

190
00:12:14,290 --> 00:12:14,930
Hurry!

191
00:12:15,980 --> 00:12:16,460
Let's go.

192
00:12:26,220 --> 00:12:27,340
I found it!

193
00:12:27,460 --> 00:12:28,650
Third Young Master, I found it!

194
00:12:40,100 --> 00:12:40,860
Help!

195
00:12:43,650 --> 00:12:44,170
Help!

196
00:12:45,050 --> 00:12:45,890
Wang Huzi,

197
00:12:46,220 --> 00:12:47,770
what are you doing in the pond?

198
00:12:50,620 --> 00:12:51,260
I'm trying to catch a fish.

199
00:12:58,650 --> 00:13:00,380
He's truly a fool.

200
00:13:00,770 --> 00:13:02,570
Wang Huzi is foolish yet ruthless.

201
00:13:03,100 --> 00:13:04,290
You and I would've been dead

202
00:13:04,290 --> 00:13:05,650
had Yansheng not given us

203
00:13:05,650 --> 00:13:06,770
a reminder.

204
00:13:08,170 --> 00:13:08,980
Yuhu, Tianlei,

205
00:13:10,410 --> 00:13:11,740
the careless hare has finally

206
00:13:12,100 --> 00:13:13,140
shown himself.

207
00:13:14,050 --> 00:13:15,810
Maybe even Wang Huzi himself

208
00:13:15,980 --> 00:13:17,100
didn't know that he was only exposed

209
00:13:17,100 --> 00:13:18,570
when he showed himself.

210
00:13:19,570 --> 00:13:20,380
Some time ago,

211
00:13:20,500 --> 00:13:21,890
Bingyan told us

212
00:13:22,050 --> 00:13:23,050
to be wary of Ke Shizhao

213
00:13:23,460 --> 00:13:24,860
when she came here.

214
00:13:24,860 --> 00:13:26,170
And now, he has given himself away.

215
00:13:26,690 --> 00:13:28,570
Bingyan is our lucky star, indeed.

216
00:13:29,020 --> 00:13:30,050
Bingyan was here before?

217
00:13:31,860 --> 00:13:32,380
Tianlei,

218
00:13:32,810 --> 00:13:34,100
why did she come to Qi Residence?

219
00:13:34,100 --> 00:13:34,740
Master,

220
00:13:35,050 --> 00:13:37,260
this is another amazing coincidence.

221
00:13:37,810 --> 00:13:39,650
Ke Shizhao sent his men
to Yangzhou in secret

222
00:13:39,650 --> 00:13:41,340
and invited Mr. Du to Qi Residence.

223
00:13:41,340 --> 00:13:42,260
They wanted to use Mr. Du

224
00:13:42,260 --> 00:13:43,690
to expose Yuhu's identity.

225
00:13:43,980 --> 00:13:44,690
However,

226
00:13:44,690 --> 00:13:45,740
at the same time, Du Bingyan

227
00:13:45,740 --> 00:13:47,770
was returning to Yangzhou
from the border town.

228
00:13:48,170 --> 00:13:49,100
She disguised herself as a man

229
00:13:49,100 --> 00:13:51,290
and followed Mr. Du to Qi Residence.

230
00:13:51,500 --> 00:13:52,500
The real Du Bingyan

231
00:13:52,500 --> 00:13:53,740
called the fake Du Bingyan

232
00:13:53,740 --> 00:13:54,740
her younger sister.

233
00:13:55,500 --> 00:13:57,380
Ke Shizhao wasn't the only one confused.

234
00:13:57,500 --> 00:13:58,170
I couldn't wrap my head

235
00:13:58,170 --> 00:13:59,650
around the situation too.

236
00:14:00,890 --> 00:14:02,860
Bingyan did offer you two

237
00:14:03,220 --> 00:14:04,220
timely help, indeed.

238
00:14:05,620 --> 00:14:06,170
Tianlei,

239
00:14:06,650 --> 00:14:08,260
when did Bingyan arrive at Linzhou?

240
00:14:09,500 --> 00:14:10,340
May 4th.

241
00:14:11,260 --> 00:14:12,620
When did she return to Yangzhou, then?

242
00:14:12,980 --> 00:14:14,020
She stayed here for two nights.

243
00:14:14,290 --> 00:14:15,050
So, it's May 6th.

244
00:14:18,410 --> 00:14:19,020
This is bad.

245
00:14:19,650 --> 00:14:20,810
They helped you guys out

246
00:14:21,050 --> 00:14:22,460
at the expense of their own matters.

247
00:14:22,740 --> 00:14:23,690
What do you mean?

248
00:14:27,020 --> 00:14:27,890
Yuan Buqu

249
00:14:28,460 --> 00:14:30,500
was following
Du Bingyan's instructions initially.

250
00:14:30,500 --> 00:14:31,530
He rushed back to Yangzhou

251
00:14:31,650 --> 00:14:33,340
after completing the task.

252
00:14:33,650 --> 00:14:34,980
He rushed there to pick Du Bingyan up.

253
00:14:35,620 --> 00:14:36,380
Now that I think about it,

254
00:14:36,770 --> 00:14:38,650
I assume he was there around May 4th.

255
00:14:39,380 --> 00:14:40,690
Seems like he had to leave empty-handed.

256
00:14:41,570 --> 00:14:42,930
I don't think so.

257
00:14:43,770 --> 00:14:44,930
I think General Yuan Buqu

258
00:14:44,930 --> 00:14:47,620
will wait for Bingyan's return.

259
00:14:49,650 --> 00:14:51,410
I'm just afraid that he has no time
to stay in Yangzhou.

260
00:14:52,100 --> 00:14:54,170
The consort selection issue
hasn't been completely resolved yet.

261
00:14:56,260 --> 00:14:57,810
What if His Majesty
summons him back to the capital?

262
00:14:57,810 --> 00:15:00,170
Even so, he'll leave a letter behind
for Bingyan.

263
00:15:03,410 --> 00:15:04,380
Although the coincidence
worked in your favor,

264
00:15:05,860 --> 00:15:07,650
I don't think it'd work in theirs.

265
00:15:21,050 --> 00:15:21,650
Fatty.

266
00:15:22,570 --> 00:15:23,380
Let's check it out.

267
00:15:26,860 --> 00:15:27,410
Sir,

268
00:15:28,460 --> 00:15:31,220
does General Yuan live here?

269
00:15:31,220 --> 00:15:31,890
I don't know.

270
00:15:33,650 --> 00:15:35,340
If so, do you know where he lives?

271
00:15:36,170 --> 00:15:36,980
I don't.

272
00:15:39,290 --> 00:15:39,890
All right then.

273
00:15:40,500 --> 00:15:41,100
Thank you.

274
00:15:43,170 --> 00:15:43,980
Thank you, sir.

275
00:16:01,050 --> 00:16:01,650
Miss Bingyan,

276
00:16:02,170 --> 00:16:04,140
we couldn't find him
even after a long search.

277
00:16:04,500 --> 00:16:05,530
This place is huge.

278
00:16:06,100 --> 00:16:07,930
