310
00:17:22,260 --> 00:17:23,090
He was an excellent storyteller.

311
00:17:23,130 --> 00:17:23,610
Yes.

312
00:17:23,610 --> 00:17:24,570
It's just that he likes
to keep us in suspense.

313
00:17:24,570 --> 00:17:25,050
That's right.

