the details of our war?

326
00:17:44,290 --> 00:17:44,940
That's right.

327
00:17:45,900 --> 00:17:46,610
Following the story,

328
00:17:46,850 --> 00:17:49,940
Marquis of the North defended
the border for several months.

329
