343
00:18:22,610 --> 00:18:24,020
Please come again tomorrow.

344
00:18:36,290 --> 00:18:37,700
Greetings, sir.

345
00:18:38,660 --> 00:18:39,220
Mister,

346
00:18:39,660 --> 00:18:40,770
how did you manage

347
00:18:40,770 --> 00:18:41,570
