366
00:19:17,940 --> 00:19:18,770
[I'll get the door.]

367
00:19:23,900 --> 00:19:24,500
Sir.

368
00:19:29,180 --> 00:19:29,770
Pingwei.

369
00:19:30,500 --> 00:19:31,220
Du Bin?

370
00:19:31,850 --> 00:19:33,020
I finally found you.

371
00:19:35,020 --> 00:19:35,770
I understand now.

372
00:19:36,850 --> 00:19:38,740
You made the storyteller

373
00:19:38,740 --> 00:19:40,420
tell our stories

374
00:19:40,420 --> 00:19:41,660
