375
00:19:42,940 --> 00:19:44,260
You're so intelligent.

376
00:19:44,940 --> 00:19:45,570
I...

377
00:19:46,500 --> 00:19:48,460
I had no choice.

378
00:19:51,220 --> 00:19:52,330
We shouldn't talk here.

379
00:19:52,610 --> 00:19:53,700
We can talk back in the residence.

380
00:19:55,770 --> 00:19:56,420
Let's return to the residence.

381
00:19:57,570 --> 00:19:58,330
Fatty, let's go.

382
00:19:58,570 --> 00:19:59,130
All right.

383
00:19:59,260 --> 00:19:59,850
Du Bin.

384
00:20:00,660 --> 00:20:01,180
Please.

385
00:20:06,900 --> 00:20:07,500
Have a seat.

386
00:20:13,660 --> 00:20:14,770
Vice General Sha, please have some tea.

387
00:20:15,020 --> 00:20:15,980
Mister, please have some tea.

388
00:20:17,500 --> 00:20:18,500
You guys may leave.

389
00:20:18,660 --> 00:20:19,220
Yes, Vice General.

390
00:20:23,770 --> 00:20:25,500
