393
00:20:30,370 --> 00:20:31,260
That's not true.

394
00:20:31,770 --> 00:20:33,500
Bingyan, you should stop mocking me.

395
00:20:34,900 --> 00:20:36,850
Maybe it's because
I've been in the capital for too long.

396
00:20:37,130 --> 00:20:38,900
I can't just slack off

397
00:20:38,900 --> 00:20:40,330
