The imperial edict hasn't been issued yet.

414
00:21:10,460 --> 00:21:11,700
I can't say for sure

415
00:21:11,700 --> 00:21:12,610
that I'll be the princess's consort yet.

416
00:21:14,740 --> 00:21:15,770
But you should tell me

417
00:21:16,130 --> 00:21:17,420
when you arrived at the capital

418
00:21:17,940 --> 00:21:19,740
and the reason
you disguised yourself as a man.

419
00:21:21,370 --> 00:21:23,330
It's a long story.

420
00:21:24,090 --> 00:21:25,130
Not long ago,

421
00:21:25,500 --> 00:21:27,130
Buqu suddenly...

422
00:21:27,130 --> 00:21:29,660
[Her Highness has arrived.]

423
00:21:31,660 --> 00:21:32,260
Pingwei,

424
00:21:32,980 --> 00:21:34,130
when the princess comes,

425
00:21:34,130 --> 00:21:35,180
tell her that I'm a medical disciple.

426
00:21:35,500 --> 00:21:36,570
Don't tell her who I am.

427
00:21:37,660 --> 00:21:38,220
All right.

428
00:21:44,420 --> 00:21:46,610
Your Highness, this is Du Bin.

429
00:21:47,020 --> 00:21:49,660
He's a medic in our military camp.

430
00:21:50,460 --> 00:21:52,130
Greetings, Your Highness. I'm Du Bin.

431
00:21:52,330 --> 00:21:53,180
Spare the formalities.

432
00:21:56,500 --> 00:21:57,180
Pingwei,

433
00:21:57,610 --> 00:21:59,500
why didn't you tell me that you had such a

