495
00:24:10,700 --> 00:24:11,810
Who are you calling silly?

496
00:24:11,810 --> 00:24:12,370
You.

497
00:24:13,220 --> 00:24:13,810
See you.

498
00:24:14,500 --> 00:24:15,050
Let's go.

499
00:24:29,330 --> 00:24:30,420
