503
00:24:53,090 --> 00:24:53,700
Buqu,

504
00:24:54,330 --> 00:24:55,660
I've finally found you.

505
00:24:55,660 --> 00:24:56,330
Pingwei?

506
00:24:57,660 --> 00:24:58,570
How did you find me?

507
00:24:59,500 --> 00:25:00,700
Why didn't you tell me

508
00:25:01,020 --> 00:25:01,980
