516
00:25:25,570 --> 00:25:26,570
No need for that.

517
00:25:26,900 --> 00:25:27,770
Tell him to leave.

518
00:25:31,570 --> 00:25:32,940
You're the future princess's consort.

519
00:25:32,940 --> 00:25:33,660
Here, have a seat.

520
00:25:33,660 --> 00:25:34,220
Buqu.

521
00:25:34,460 --> 00:25:35,020
You should sit down.

522
00:25:35,530 --> 00:25:36,330
You should sit down first.

523
00:25:38,660 --> 00:25:40,220
Please don't call me that again.

524
00:25:42,130 --> 00:25:43,220
All right.

525
00:25:45,130 --> 00:25:45,810
