536
00:26:11,530 --> 00:26:13,330
without even needing to see the patient.

537
00:26:14,980 --> 00:26:15,500
Why don't you give it a try?

538
00:26:18,370 --> 00:26:18,980
How did it go?

539
00:26:19,530 --> 00:26:20,130
Mister,

540
00:26:20,460 --> 00:26:21,370
you're intelligent indeed.

541
00:26:24,020 --> 00:26:24,610
Bingyan,

542
00:26:26,660 --> 00:26:27,850
I already told Buqu about it.

543
00:26:27,850 --> 00:26:29,220
You just need to stand here.

544
00:26:29,460 --> 00:26:30,220
This is my plan.

545
00:26:38,460 --> 00:26:39,020
Sir, please.

546
00:26:39,020 --> 00:26:39,530
Please.

547
00:26:41,530 --> 00:26:42,130
Buqu,

548
00:26:42,610 --> 00:26:44,570
this is the student of the divine healer.

549
00:26:45,220 --> 00:26:46,090
My name is Guo Hai.

550
00:26:46,530 --> 00:26:47,610
Greetings, General.

551
00:26:48,700 --> 00:26:49,570
Spare the formalities.

552
00:26:49,570 --> 00:26:50,420
All right.

553
00:26:50,420 --> 00:26:51,570
Hurry and give Buqu a diagnosis.

554
00:26:58,090 --> 00:26:58,850
General,

555
00:26:59,180 --> 00:26:59,980
please remain seated

556
00:27:00,260 --> 00:27:01,220
