557
00:27:01,770 --> 00:27:02,940
I'll relay my master's message

558
00:27:02,940 --> 00:27:04,740
to you.

559
00:27:05,460 --> 00:27:05,980
All right.

560
00:27:16,090 --> 00:27:16,810
